## MapboxMapProps.iframeWindow property

The window object of the iframe where the map should rendered. Must have mapboxgl loaded. If not provided or mapboxgl not loaded, the map will be rendered in the parent window.

**Signature:**

```typescript
iframeWindow?: Window;
```
